OL,7,FThe number of visas granted to
OL,8,Ffinancially dependent relatives and
OL,9,Fpartners of students coming to study
OL,10,Fin the UK has fallen sharply compared
OL,11,Fto last year, new Home Office figures
OL,12,Fshow.
OL,14,FIn the first six months of this year,
OL,15,Fvisas granted to dependants of
OL,16,Foverseas students tumbled by 81% to
OL,17,F11,675 compared to the same period in
OL,18,F2023.
