OL,7,FIt follows plans announced in May 2023
OL,8,Fby the Conservative government to
OL,9,Fblock international sponsored students
OL,10,Ffrom bringing dependants with them to
OL,11,Fthe UK.
OL,13,FThe number of health and care worker
OL,14,Fvisas granted was also 26% lower
OL,15,Fcompared to the same period last year.
OL,17,FThis comes after the previous
OL,18,Fgovernment introduced changes in
OL,19,FMarch, which restricted overseas care
OL,20,Fworkers from bringing relatives with
OL,21,Fthem to the UK.
