OL,7,FThe statistics have also shown a four-
OL,8,Ffold increase in the number of
OL,9,Fdecisions being made on all asylum
OL,10,Fclaims between June 2023 and June 2024.
OL,12,FAccording to the Home Office
OL,13,Fstatistics, over 97,000 applied for
OL,14,Fasylum in the UK between June 2023 and
OL,15,FJune 2024 - a drop of 8% compared to
OL,16,Fthe previous year, which the
OL,17,Fdepartment said is due to a decrease
OL,18,Fin claims from Albanian small boat
OL,19,Farrivals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
