OL,7,FThe number of decisions on asylum
OL,8,Fapplications in the same period was
OL,9,Ffour times higher than the previous
OL,10,Fyear, which the Home Office attributes
OL,11,Fto more asylum decision makers and
OL,12,Fincreased productivity.
OL,14,FThe figures also found less decisions
OL,15,Fresulted in grants of protection
OL,16,Fcompared to the year before, down from
OL,17,F71% to 58%.
