OL,7,FThe figures come follow the home
OL,8,Fsecretary's announcement of new
OL,9,Fmeasures to tackle illegal
OL,10,Fimmigration, including hiring more
OL,11,Fspecialist officers to dismantle
OL,12,Fsmuggling gangs, and increasing
OL,13,Fdeportation flights.
OL,15,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper insisted
OL,16,Fthe Home Office is taking "strong and
OL,17,Fclear steps to... ensure the rules are
OL,18,Frespected and enforced", and said she
OL,19,Fis trying to achieve the highest
OL,20,Fremoval rates since 2018.
