OL,7,FRefugee charity Care4Calais CEO Steve
OL,8,FSmith said: "The new government
OL,9,Fcontinuing to invest in border
OL,10,Fsecurity rather than workable
OL,11,Fsolutions is repeating the mistakes of
OL,12,Fthe last government.
OL,14,F"The evidence shows that these so-
OL,15,Fcalled deterrents don't work. They do
OL,16,Fnothing to reduce Channel crossings,
OL,17,Fthey just force people to take greater
OL,18,Frisks to do so.
