OL,8,Fvowed to introduce a scheme where some
OL,9,Findividuals entering the UK illegally
OL,10,Fwould be deported to Rwanda - but this
OL,11,Fwas scrapped by Prime Minister Sir
OL,12,FKeir Starmer just two days into his
OL,13,Ftime in office.
